    "Its goal is to identify all gene features, including protein-coding sequences, noncoding RNAs, pseudogenes, and their variants.",
    "The genome sequence is also included in the dataset.",
    "CellxGene Corpus [340] is a broad single-cell corpus that contains 789 cell types from 1,219 datasets.",
    "The overall cell expression number reaches over 72 million.",
    "Biobank [354] provides a summary of all the information gathered by UK Biobank on 500,000 participants which contain imaging, genetics, health linkages, biomarkers, activity monitor, online questionnaires, repeat baseline assessments, etc."
